    </TD>
    <TD>
      12 km
    </TD>
  </TR>
  <TR>
    <TD>
      Length of cable:
    </TD>
    <TD>
      250 km
    </TD>
  </TR>
  <TR>
    <TD>
      Main reasons for choosing HVDC system:
    </TD>
    <TD>
      Sea crossing
    </TD>
  </TR>
</TABLE>
