<HTML>
<HEAD>
  <META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Word 1.0Z">
  <META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="ABB Power Systems AB">
  <TITLE>ConTune AC Filter</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="paper.jpg">
<P>
<A NAME="DDE_LINK2"><IMG ALIGN=RIGHT BORDER=0 HEIGHT=30 SRC="abblog5.gif"
    alt=""> <IMG SRC="powlog1.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></A>
<P>
<IMG width=100% SRC="redline.gif" alt=" ">
<H2>
  ConTune AC filter
</H2>
<P>
<CENTER>
  <IMG align=center SRC="sk6557.gif">
  <P>
  <I>Principle of automatic tuning</I>
</CENTER>
<H4>
  The ConTune filter has a high quality factor for the best filtering performance
  and the lowest possible losses. The tuning frequency is automatically adjusted
  to provide prefect tuning irrespective of network frequency excursions and
  filter component variations.
</H4>
<H4>
  The ConTune filter offers:
  <UL>
    <LI>
      Maximum filter performance even at large frequency excursions
    <LI>
      Lower losses
    <LI>
      Less space
    <LI>
      No moving parts.
  </UL>
</H4>
<P>
<TABLE>
  <TR>
    <TD>
      <H3>
	Automatic tuning control
      </H3>
      <H4>
	The high performance of the ConTune filter is achieved by using a filter
	reactor with variable inductance.
      </H4>
      <H4>
	The variable inductance is achieved with an iron core which is placed inside
	the reactor. Around the iron core there is a control winding. By feeding
	a variable direct current into the control winding, the total magnetic flux
	in the reactor is influenced, thereby changing the inductance. Control of
	the inductance is characterized by its high linearity.
      </H4>
      <P>
    </TD>
    <TD>
      <CENTER>
	<IMG SRC="sk6251.gif">
      </CENTER>
      <P>
      <I>Tuned reactor</I>
    </TD>
  </TR>
</TABLE>
<H3>
  Experience
</H3>
<H4>
  A prototype 11th harmonic AC filter has been in operation at the Lindome
  station of the Konti-Skan HVDC Link since December 1993. Experience of this
  has been excellent. A ConTune filter will be installed in 1996 in the Celilo
  station of the Pacific Intertie HVDC transmission.
</H4>
<P>
<CENTER>
  <IMG SRC="l36872.jpg">
</CENTER>
<P ALIGN=Center>
<I>Prototype ConTune installation at Lindome</I> 
  <HR>
<P>
<CENTER>
  <IMG SRC="abbhand.gif" ALIGN=TOP> | <A HREF="home.htm">ABB Power Systems
  Home Page</A> | <A HREF="http://www.abb.se">ABB Sweden</A> |
</CENTER>
<P>
  <HR>
