<B>Series Compensation References </B>
<P>
ABB Power Systems has a leading position with 60% market share
in the series capacitor field.
<P>
Over the years our technical lead has permitted us to carry development
forward, presenting, as the first, technical solutions which later
became the standard among manufactures of series capacitors.
<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="worldmap.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"> 
