<TITLE>ABB Power Systems-SVC Mechanical Design</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Word 1.0Z">
<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="ABB Power Systems AB">
</HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="paper.jpg">

<P>
<IMG ALIGN=RIGHT BORDER=0 HEIGHT=30 SRC="abblog5.gif" alt="">
<IMG SRC="powlog1.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM">.
<P>
<IMG width=100% SRC="redline.gif" alt=" "> <BR>
<B>SVC Electromechanical Design</B> 
<P>
ABB Power Systems has the resources to supply complete Static
Var Compensators on a turnkey basis.<BR>
With our computer programs, we can determine the optimum position
of an SVC in your network. We can also optimise the flow of active
and reactive power with respect to production costs and transmission
losses, study the influence of load variations from, for example,
rolling mills, arc furnaces and motor drives, and propose measures
for reducing voltage variations.
<P>
The items included in our SVCs are to a large extent manufactured
in our own factories, either at the parent company in Sweden or
at the plants of our subsidiaries in Sweden and elsewhere.<BR>
With the aid of advanced computer programs for planning and control,
we can maintain short delivery times and effectively control all
the activities associated with the complete turnkey projects.
<P>
