<HEAD>

<TITLE>ABB Power Systems-SVC references</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Word 1.0Z">
<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="ABB Power Systems AB">
</HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="paper.jpg">

<P>
<IMG ALIGN=RIGHT BORDER=0 HEIGHT=30 SRC="abblog5.gif" alt="">
<IMG SRC="powlog1.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM">.
<P>
<IMG width=100% SRC="redline.gif" alt=" "> <BR>
<B>Static Var Compensation References</B> 
<P>
ABB Power Systems has a leading position with around 50% market
share in the field of static var compensation.
<P>
The company became aware of the importance of effective and rapid
control of reactive power very early on. We were the first company
in the world to commission a large commercial thyristor-switched
capacitor installation.
<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="worldmap.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"> 
<P>
| <A HREF="r23.htm">North America</A> | <A HREF="r24.htm">South America</A>
| <A HREF="r25.htm">Europe</A> | <A HREF="r26.htm">Africa</A>
| <A HREF="r27.htm">Asia</A> | <A HREF="r28.htm">Australia</A>
| </CENTER><HR>

<P>
The research started at our company in 1967 and the world's first
commercial installation of thyristor-switched capacitors (TSC)
for an industrial application was delivered in 1972. Since then
have the number of installations increased to 280 in 46 different
countries, with the totally installed power of more than 30.000
Mvar.<HR>

<P>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="abbhand.gif" ALIGN=TOP> |<A HREF="home.htm">ABB Power Systems Home Page</A>
| <A HREF="http://www.abb.se">ABB Sweden</A> | </CENTER><HR>

<P>
<A HREF="copyrajt.htm">Copyright </A>ABB Power Systems Sweden 1995. <BR>
<B>Latest updated 18-Mars-1996</B> 
</BODY>

