<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>ABB Infosystems Dataskerhet / Lnkar</TITLE>
<meta name="description" content="ABB Infosystems skerhetsrelaterade lnkar">
<meta name="keywords" content="ABB Infosystems, skerhet, dataskerhet, security links, SATAN extensions">  
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="../infback.JPG" BGCOLOR="#ffffff" LINK="#FF0A11" VLINK="#7E0B06">
<IMG ALIGN=Right SRC="../logo.gif" WIDTH=116 HEIGHT=55>
<P>




<TABLE CELLSPACING=4 CELLPADDING=2 BORDER=0>
<TR>
<TD  height=120 WIDTH=180>&nbsp;</TD>
<TD WIDTH=*>&nbsp;</TD>

<TR VALIGN=LEFT>
<TD WIDTH=180>
<A HREF="welcome.html"><IMG SRC="../secbt+.JPG" WIDTH=140 border=0 HEIGHT=35></A><br>
<IMG SRC="servpic.JPG" WIDTH=140 HEIGHT=120><P><BR>
</TD>
	
<TD WIDTH=400>
<FONT SIZE=+2>Skerhetsrelaterade lnkar</FONT>
<HR>
<P>
Vi anvnder sjlva Internet intensivt i vrt arbete. Vr frmsta uppgift r att finna en realistisk hotbild, baserad p kunskap spridd p Internet. Denna hotbild ligger sedan till grund fr vrt skerhetsarbete. Hr presenterar vi ett antal ppna kllor om datorskerhet. 
<P>
Vi r medlemmar i ISACA - Information Systems Audit and Control Association
<P>

<BLOCKQUOTE><LI> <A HREF="http://www.isaca.org">ISACA/F - homepage</A> 
<LI><A HREF="http://www.isaca.org/standard/general.htm"> ISACA/F - General Standards for Information Systems Auditing </A>
<LI> <A HREF="http://www.isaca.org/cobit.htm">COBIT - Control objectives for Information and Related Technology</A> </BLOCKQUOTE>
<P>

Ett urval informationskllor
<P>
