<LI><A HREF="http://www.punkt.se/Bransch/Datorer%2C%20telekom%20%26%20Internet/Tj%E4nster/Dators%E4kerhet/">www.punkt.se Tjnster/Dataskerhet (in swedish)</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.yahoo.com/Computers_and_Internet/Security_and_Encryption/"> Yahoo - Security and Encryption</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.cert.org">CERT Coordination Center</A> 
