<LI><A HREF="http://www.trouble.org/survey">Dan Farmer: Shall we dust Moscow</A> 
<LI><A HREF="ftp://ftp.win.tue.nl/pub/security/index.html">Wietse's collection of tools and papers</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.sophist.demon.co.uk/ping/index.html">The Ping o' Death Page</A> 
