<IMG SRC="servpic.JPG" ALT="Data theft" WIDTH=140 HEIGHT=120><P></TD>
	
<TD WIDTH=400>
<FONT SIZE=+2>IT- Threat or new possibilities</FONT>
<HR>
<P>
ABB Infosystems Security Services group was formed in order to meet the increasing demand for IT-security, both within and outside the ABB group. 
We have experience in fields like auditing standards, operating systems, network communication and computer security. 
