"Vxa med frndring" (Growth through change) is our very own<P>
 process of change, one which involves all our staff and shapes <P>
the way we work.Some of the keywords in our process of change are: <P>
process orientation, project focusing, competence enhancement, <P>
quality assurance, operational control and customer care. <P>
Our organisation has a clear-cut<IMG ALIGN=Right SRC="vmflog.JPG" WIDTH=159 HEIGHT=92 border=0><P>
customer bias with few hierarchical levels<P>
immense flexibility and decentralised<P>
 responsibility.
