<TD WIDTH=400>
<FONT SIZE=+2>Why and how to contact us</FONT>
<HR>
<P>
Everything changes fast. The security knowledge that was valid a only a few years ago, is obsolete today. Just as in the data communication and the Internet. <p>
As technology and information flows change, new vulnerabilities are introduced.
<P>
Our aim is to create advanced security solutions and at the same time have firsthand knowledge of the new methods used by crackers to break the computer security. 
ABB Infosystems Security Services group was formed in order to meet the increasing demand for IT-security, both within and outside the ABB group. <BR>
<dd>We have experience in fields like auditing standards, operating systems, network communication and computer security. 
<P>&nbsp;<P>
