<TD WIDTH=400>
<FONT SIZE=+2>Security related links</FONT>
<HR>
<P>
We make intensive use of Internet in our work. Our main aim is to find a realistic danger level, based on knowledge available on the net. This level is then used to determine the actions needed to create an acceptable security standard. 
<P>
We are members of ISACA - Information Systems Audit and Control Association
<P>

<BLOCKQUOTE><LI> <A HREF="http://www.isaca.org">ISACA/F - homepage</A> 
<LI><A HREF="http://www.isaca.org/standard/general.htm"> ISACA/F - General Standards for Information Systems Auditing </A>
