<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>ABB Infosystems Security / Internet Exposure</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="../infback.JPG" BGCOLOR="#ffffff" LINK="#FF0A11" VLINK="#7E0B06">
<IMG ALIGN=Right SRC="../logo.gif" ALT=" ABB Logotype" WIDTH=116 HEIGHT=55>
<P>




<TABLE CELLSPACING=4 CELLPADDING=2 BORDER=0>
<TR>
<TD  height=120 WIDTH=180>&nbsp;</TD>
<TD WIDTH=*>&nbsp;</TD>

<TR VALIGN=LEFT>
<TD WIDTH=180>
<A HREF="_welcome.html"><IMG SRC="../secbte+.JPG" ALT="Security" WIDTH=140 border=0 HEIGHT=35></A><br>
<IMG SRC="inet.JPG" ALT="Exposure" WIDTH="140" HEIGHT="120" BORDER="0"><P></TD>
	
<TD WIDTH=400>I N T E R N E T &nbsp; E X P O S U R E
<P>

<FONT SIZE=+2>To be seen and heard on the net </FONT>
<HR>
<P>
Market Exposure with regard to Internet could mean different things. It is possible to measure the company presence on
the net and compare it to the competitors, and for each market compare the numbers of references given by search engines
and link pages. It is possible to analyse competitors presence in different projects by searching links and examine the
findings. Customers and partners often enter links to their manufactures. 
<P>

Our objective in this area is to help our customers to achieve an advantage by honest means. After we have evaluated the
company presence on the net, we will report our findings and suggestions for changes in the web pages, and the way of
spreading information. 
<P>

<HR>
<P>

</td>

<tr>
<td WIDTH=180><A HREF="../seinfbe.html"><IMG ALIGN=Left SRC="../pil.JPG" WIDTH=31 HEIGHT=19 BORDER=0></A></td>
