<P><A HREF="topics/index.html"><FONT SIZE=-1>Phone Numbers</FONT></A></P>

<P><A HREF="departments/index.html"><FONT SIZE=-1>Departments</FONT></A></P>

<P><A HREF="publications/index.html"><FONT SIZE=-1>Publications</FONT></A></P>

<P><A HREF="related.html"><FONT SIZE=-1>Other Sites</FONT></A></TD>
<TD WIDTH="75%"><P>Winter is Here!</P>

<P><STRONG>There is no Snow Emergency in effect.</STRONG> Information on
<A HREF="departments/public-works/snow.html">Snow Emergency parking restrictions</A>
is available on-line, or call 348-SNOW for a recorded message.</P>

<P><HR ALIGN=LEFT></P>

<P><STRONG>Due to high levels of snow accumulation, Minneapolis has banned
parking on the even side of residential streets for the winter.</STRONG>
The ban is in effect until April 1, 1997. Please read the full <A HREF=
"/publications/news-release/pkgban96.html">news release</A> for details.</P>

<P><FONT SIZE=-1>Please set your bookmark here for up-to-date Snow Emergency
information.</FONT></TD></TR>
<TR>
<TD VALIGN="TOP" HEIGHT="135"><P>&nbsp;</P>

<P><STRONG><FONT SIZE=+2>What's New</FONT></STRONG></P>

<P>Find out how you can <A HREF="plan.html">put yourself into the plan</A>
and fight crime in Minneapolis.</P>

<P>The <A HREF="departments/assessor/index.html">Department of Assessor</A>
has made available information about homesteading.</TD></TR>
