<HTML><HEAD>    <TITLE>Code of Ordinances Help Page</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff"><H1><CENTER>City of Minneapolis<BR>Code of Ordinances</CENTER></H1><H3><I>Our code of ordinances is maintained by Municipal Code Corporation.By clicking the continue button below, you will jump to their web site.To get back to the City's web site, use the &quot;back&quot; button on yourbrowser.</I></H3><I><BR>Note: In order to browse or search the City ordinances, you must be usinga graphical web browser such as Netscape and have the graphics turned on.<BR><P><CENTER></I><A HREF="http://www.municode.com/folio.pgi/11490.NFO?"><IMG SRC="mplshome.gif" WIDTH="89" HEIGHT="39" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"></A><A HREF="http://www.ci.mpls.mn.us/"><IMG SRC="forward.gif" WIDTH="89" HEIGHT="39" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"></A></CENTER><P><HR><H2>How to use the database</H2>The code of ordinances page should look like this: <BR><P><CENTER><IMG SRC="code.gif" WIDTH="360" HEIGHT="289" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" ALIGN="BOTTOM" ALT="MCC's Code of Ordinances page"></CENTER><P>To search for <B>keywords</B>, press the <IMG SRC="query.gif" WIDTH="55" HEIGHT="39" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3" ALT="Query"> button.Type the words you wish to search for and press &quot;search.&quot; <BR>Your browser will display the number of &quot;hits.&quot; To see the text,press the <IMG SRC="doc.gif" WIDTH="54" HEIGHT="40" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3" ALT="Document"> button. <H3>Hints: </H3><UL>  <LI>Use quotes around phrases like &quot;city clerk's office&quot; tosearch for the phrase.   <LI>Use the booleans <B>and, or, not</B> in searches like <I>mayor andcouncil</I> or <I>mayor not council.<BR></I>Use and asterisk (*) in place of suffix endings. for example, <I>admin*</I>will find administration, administrator, etc. </UL><P><CENTER><HR></CENTER><P>To <B>browse</B> the table of contents, press the <IMG SRC="contents.gif"WIDTH="54" HEIGHT="39" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3" ALT="Contents">button. <BR><BR>You will see a table of contents page for the City of Minneapolis. Clickon the plus <IMG SRC="plus.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="10" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"> or minus <IMG SRC="minus.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="10" ALIGN="BOTTOM"NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"> images to expand or collapse portions of the contents.You can also use the control bar <IMG SRC="level10.gif" WIDTH="236" HEIGHT="20" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"> to show levels of detail.<BR><BR>Click on any chapter, article or division to see the actual text. <BR><BR><HR><BR><P><CENTER><A HREF="http://www.municode.com/folio.pgi/11490.NFO?"><IMG SRC="mplshome.gif" WIDTH="89" HEIGHT="39" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"></A><A HREF="http://www.ci.mpls.mn.us/"><IMG SRC="forward.gif" WIDTH="89" HEIGHT="39" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"></A></CENTER><P><HR>Questions or comments? E-mail <A HREF="mailto:opa_mpls@ci.mpls.mn.us">opa_mpls@ci.mpls.mn.us</A></BODY></HTML>
