<HTML>
<HEAD>
  <META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Adobe PageMill 2.0 Mac">
  <TITLE>96-97 Minneapolis Calendar of Events</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY TEXT="#04006b" BGCOLOR="#ffffff">

<P><A NAME="top"></A> <TABLE BORDER="0" CELLSPACING="2" CELLPADDING="0">
<TR>
<TD VALIGN="TOP"><IMG SRC="/pict/sails.gif" ALT="logo" ALIGN="BOTTOM"></TD>
<TD VALIGN="CENTER"><H1 ALIGN=RIGHT>City of Minneapolis</H1>

<H2 ALIGN=RIGHT>Calendar of Events<BR>
From the 1996-97 City Calendar</H2>
</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
<BR>
<BR>
<HR ALIGN=LEFT><A HREF="/index.html">Home</A> | <A HREF="/hot/index.html">What's
Hot</A> | <A HREF="/events.html">Events</A> | <A HREF="/topics/index.html">Topics</A>
| <A HREF="/departments/index.html">Departments</A> | <A HREF="/publications/index.html">Publications</A>
| <A HREF="/related.html">Other Sites</A> <HR ALIGN=LEFT></P>

<P ALIGN=CENTER>The events listed below are from the 1996-97 Minneapolis
