<BR>
The Solid Waste and Recycling Holiday Policy is in effect on certain holidays.
Collections normally falling on or after Thanksgiving, Christmas, New Year's,
Memorial Day, Independence Day, or Labor Day will be one day later. Questions?
Call 673-2917 (TTY 673-2157).</P>

