<TD VALIGN="TOP">U of M Spring Classes begin</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
</P>

<P>Yard work is just around the corner. Remember that a dull lawnmower blade
tears grass. This results in brown, damaged grass tips. By sharpening your
blade at a nearby hardware store, you can mow faster and keep a greener
lawn.</P>

