<P>Month-long street sweeping begins in mid-October. &quot;No Parking&quot;
signs are posted the day before sweeping. Vehicles not moved are towed.
After you rake leaves, consider composting instead of bagging them. For
composting information, call 673-2917 (TTY 673-2157).</P>

