<P><HR ALIGN=LEFT></P>

<H2 ALIGN=CENTER>Where are the rest of the months?</H2>

<P ALIGN=CENTER>So that we can include snow emergency information, the City
calendar runs from November through October. When the 1997-98 calendar is
published in early November, its events will be posted on this site. To
get a printed copy of the City's 1996-97 calendar, which includes these
events and other important City information, <A HREF="mailto:%20opa_mpls@ci.mpls.mn.us">E-mail</A>
your name and snail mail address.</P>

