<DOCHDR>
http://www.ci.mpls.mn.us:80/departments/public-works/solid-waste/compost.html 198.174.235.51 19970121013936 text/html 11853
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Tue, 21 Jan 1997 01:41:23 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 11681
