<H3>EMERGENCIES</H3>

<P><I>Call </I><B>9-1-1</B><I> if you need police, fire or ambulance service to
respond to an event. Also call </I><B>9-1-1</B><I> to report suspicious events.
It does not have to be an emergency. Deaf and hard-of-hearing persons have direct
access to emergency services by calling </I><B>9-1-1 </B><I>on their TDD.</I>

