<HEAD>

<TITLE>City Coordinator</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<!-- #include "city_head.incl"
	#MY_BGCOLOR#="ffffff"
	#MY_HEADER#="City Coordinator"
-->
<BODY bgcolor="#ffffff">

<TABLE border=0>
<TR>
	<TD valign=top><IMG SRC="/pict/sails.gif" alt="logo"></TD>
	<TD valign=center><H1 align=right>City of Minneapolis</H1>
	<H2 align=right>City Coordinator</H2></TD>
</TR></TABLE>

<!-- end include -->

<!-- #include "city_navbar.incl" -->
<P><HR>

<A HREF="/index.html">Home</A>
| <A HREF="/hot/index.html">What's Hot</A>
| <A HREF="/events.html">Events</A>
| <A HREF="/topics/index.html">Topics</A>
| <A HREF="/departments/index.html">Departments</A>
| <A HREF="/publications/index.html">Publications</A>
| <A HREF="/related.html">Other Sites</A>

<HR>
<!-- end include -->

<P>The City Coordinator is responsible for providing leadership and direction in
the coordination of Minneapolis City government within the general guidelines
established by the City Charter, the <A
HREF="/departments/mayor/index.html">Mayor</A> and the <A
HREF="/departments/city-council/index.html">City Council</A>. The Coordinator
advises the Mayor and the Council regarding the impact of elected official's
policy decisions, while overseeing representation of City interests in
metropolitan, county, state and federal activities.

<P>Some major areas of accountability for the Coordinator are: 
<OL>
	<LI>Acts as an advisor and consultant to the <A
	HREF="/departments/mayor/index.html">Mayor</A> and the <A
	HREF="/departments/city-council/index.html">City Council</A> and makes
	recommendations relating to projects, policies and programs;

	<P><LI>Oversees financial operations and participates in the development of
	the City's annual budget for presentation to the City Council;

	<P><LI>Keeps the Mayor and City Council informed of all important
	developments which may affect the administration of the City;

	<P><LI>Coordinates ongoing City projects, policies and programs established by
	the Mayor or City Council; and

	<P><LI>Supervises and provides direction to department heads of <A
	HREF="/departments/city-coordinator/communications/index.html">Communications</A>,
	<A HREF="/departments/city-coordinator/hr/index.html">Human Resources</A>, <A
	HREF="/departments/city-coordinator/finance/index.html">Finance</A>, <A
	HREF="/departments/city-coordinator/operations/index.html">Operations &amp;
	Regulatory Services</A> and <A
	HREF="/departments/city-coordinator/igr.html">Intergovernmental Relations
	&amp; Quality Coordination</A>.
</OL>

<HR>

<ADDRESS>
<P><B>City Coordinator</B><BR>
City Hall, Room 301M<BR>
350 5 St S<BR>
Minneapolis, MN 55415-1376
</ADDRESS>

<P><B>Phone Number</B><BR>
(612) 673-2032<BR>


