<TITLE>Convention Center</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<!-- #include "city_head.incl"
	#MY_BGCOLOR#="ffffff"
	#MY_HEADER#="Convention Center"
-->
<BODY bgcolor="#ffffff">

<TABLE border=0>
<TR>
	<TD valign=top><IMG SRC="/pict/sails.gif" alt="logo"></TD>
	<TD valign=center><H1 align=right>City of Minneapolis</H1>
	<H2 align=right>Convention Center</H2></TD>
</TR></TABLE>

<!-- end include -->

<!-- #include "city_navbar.incl" -->
<P><HR>

<A HREF="/index.html">Home</A>
| <A HREF="/hot/index.html">What's Hot</A>
| <A HREF="/events.html">Events</A>
| <A HREF="/topics/index.html">Topics</A>
| <A HREF="/departments/index.html">Departments</A>
| <A HREF="/publications/index.html">Publications</A>
| <A HREF="/related.html">Other Sites</A>

<HR>
<!-- end include -->

<P>The objective of the Minneapolis Convention Center is to generate economic
activity in Minneapolis by providing facilities and service for conventions and
for trade and consumer shows. It is also a site for local religious, corporate,
and social activities for both individuals and companies. Together, these all
contribute to the cultural, economic, and social health of Minneapolis.

<P>This facility, in addition to its 280,000-square-foot exhibit hall, has a
28,000-square-foot ballroom as well as 54 meeting rooms which vary in size from
350 square feet to 15,000 square feet. The meeting space is tastefully decorated
with carpeting, wall finishes, and lighting. Full in-house food and beverage
service is available.

<P>Individuals and local organizations are welcome to rent convention center
facilities for meetings, special events, social gatherings, weddings, etc.
Inquiries for rental may be made up to 18 months in advance.

<P>

<HR>

<ADDRESS>
<P><B>Convention Center</B><BR>
1301 2 Av S<BR>
Minneapolis, MN 55403-2781
</ADDRESS>

<P><B>Phone Number</B><BR>
(612) 335-6000


