<HTML>
<HEAD>

<TITLE>Emergency Preparedness</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<!-- #include "city_head.incl"
	#MY_BGCOLOR#="ffffff"
	#MY_HEADER#="Emergency Preparedness"
-->
<BODY bgcolor="#ffffff">

<TABLE border=0>
<TR>
	<TD valign=top><IMG SRC="/pict/sails.gif" alt="logo"></TD>
	<TD valign=center><H1 align=right>City of Minneapolis</H1>
	<H2 align=right>Emergency Preparedness</H2></TD>
</TR></TABLE>

<!-- end include -->

<!-- #include "city_navbar.incl" -->
<P><HR>

<A HREF="/index.html">Home</A>
| <A HREF="/hot/index.html">What's Hot</A>
| <A HREF="/events.html">Events</A>
| <A HREF="/topics/index.html">Topics</A>
| <A HREF="/departments/index.html">Departments</A>
| <A HREF="/publications/index.html">Publications</A>
| <A HREF="/related.html">Other Sites</A>

<HR>
<!-- end include -->

<P>The function of this department is to maximize the level of preparation for
major emergencies.

<P>Their activities as they relate to the public include:

<UL>
	<P><LI>Responding to questions about shelters and appropriate action to take
	if threatening conditions are developing such as weather, flooding, etc.

	<P><LI>Responding to questions or complaints about warning sirens.

	<P><LI>Coordinating assistance to disaster victims.

	<P><LI>Providing public education programs on disasters including: providing
	literature on disaster preparedness, making presentations to schools,
nursing
	homes, and other groups on disaster response procedures. Educational videos
	on what to do in case of severe weather are available for free rental.
</UL>

<P>

<HR>

<ADDRESS>
<B>Emergency Preparedness</B><BR>
City Hall, Room 230<BR>
350 5 St S<BR>
Minneapolis, MN 55415-1387
</ADDRESS>

<P><B>Phone Number</B><BR>
(612) 673-2870


