<HEAD>

<TITLE>Finance</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<!-- #include "city_head.incl"
	#MY_BGCOLOR#="ffffff"
	#MY_HEADER#="Finance"
-->
<BODY bgcolor="#ffffff">

<TABLE border=0>
<TR>
	<TD valign=top><IMG SRC="/pict/sails.gif" alt="logo"></TD>
	<TD valign=center><H1 align=right>City of Minneapolis</H1>
	<H2 align=right>Finance</H2></TD>
</TR></TABLE>

<!-- end include -->

<!-- #include "city_navbar.incl" -->
<P><HR>

<A HREF="/index.html">Home</A>
| <A HREF="/hot/index.html">What's Hot</A>
| <A HREF="/events.html">Events</A>
| <A HREF="/topics/index.html">Topics</A>
| <A HREF="/departments/index.html">Departments</A>
| <A HREF="/publications/index.html">Publications</A>
| <A HREF="/related.html">Other Sites</A>

<HR>
<!-- end include -->

<P>The Finance Department's primary function is to ensure that all financial
transactions of <A HREF="/departments/index.html">City departments</A>, boards
and agencies are carried out according to dictates of the City Charter, State
Statutes, and principles of sound financial management.

<P>The Finance Department of the City Coordinator's Office is made up of six
divisions:

<DL>
	<DT><B>Administration: (612) 673-2577</B>
	<DD>Administers all Finance Department activities, including coordinating
	other divisions and interaction with the Minneapolis Community Development
	Agency.

	<DT><BR><B>Budget &amp; Evaluation: (612) 673-3007</B>
	<DD>The <A HREF="budget.html">Budget &amp; Evaluation Office</A> provides the
	<A HREF="/departments/mayor/index.html">Mayor</A>, <A
	HREF="/departments/city-council/index.html">City Council</A>, and operating
	departments with budgetary analysis and evaluation services.

	<DT><BR><B>Accounting: (612) 673-2608</B>
	<DD>Prepares the City's comprehensive annual financial report; maintains
	City's core financial system; distributes systems reports. Provides technical
	assistance and support for Finance Department microcomputer systems. Provides
	a variety of accounting services for various departments of the City, as well
	as boards, commissions and joint ventures.

	<DT><BR><B>Payroll &amp; Disbursements: (612) 673-2557</B>
	<DD>Provides processing services required for successful operations and
	control of the central payroll system; processes encumbrances and vendor
	payments.

	<DT><BR><B>Treasury: (612) 673-2311</B>
	<DD>Directs and coordinates receipting, processing, depositing, documenting,
	investing and disbursing of all monies of the City and its agencies with
	specific attention to safety, security, and internal controls.

	<DT><BR><B>Purchasing: (612) 673-2500</B>
	<DD>Procures required equipment, supplies, and services for City departments,
	the <A HREF="/departments/other/parks.html">Park Board</A>, and the <A
	HREF="/departments/other/library.html">Library Board</A>.
</DL>

<HR>

<ADDRESS>
<P><B>Finance Department</B><BR>
City Hall, Room 301M<BR>
350 5 St S<BR>
Minneapolis, MN 55415-1376
</ADDRESS>


