Catalog Information                      (612) 372-6529

Catalog Remote Access
  1200 BPS Modem                         (612) 332-5135
  2400 BPS Modem                         (612) 332-5223

Fax                                      (612) 372-6623
<STRONG>INFORM</STRONG> (fee-based research)              (612) 372-6636
