<HEAD>

<TITLE>Neighborhood Revitalization Program</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<!-- #include "city_head.incl"
	#MY_BGCOLOR#="ffffff"
	#MY_HEADER#="Neighborhood Revitalization Program"
-->
<BODY bgcolor="#ffffff">

<TABLE border=0>
<TR>
	<TD valign=top><IMG SRC="/pict/sails.gif" alt="logo"></TD>
	<TD valign=center><H1 align=right>City of Minneapolis</H1>
	<H2 align=right>Neighborhood Revitalization Program</H2></TD>
</TR></TABLE>

<!-- end include -->

<!-- #include "city_navbar.incl" -->
<P><HR>

<A HREF="/index.html">Home</A>
| <A HREF="/hot/index.html">What's Hot</A>
| <A HREF="/events.html">Events</A>
| <A HREF="/topics/index.html">Topics</A>
| <A HREF="/departments/index.html">Departments</A>
| <A HREF="/publications/index.html">Publications</A>
| <A HREF="/related.html">Other Sites</A>

<HR>
<!-- end include -->

<P>The Neighborhood Revitalization Program is a long-term commitment by the City
of Minneapolis, School Board, <A HREF="/departments/other/parks.html">Park
Board</A>, <A HREF="/departments/other/library.html">Library Board</A>, <A
HREF="http://www.co.hennepin.mn.us">Hennepin County</A>, and other participating
organizations to:

<UL>
	<LI>Revitalize neighborhoods through cooperative, coordinated service
	planning and delivery from all city, county, and other public agencies and
	private organizations.

	<P>

	<LI>Assist neighborhoods to identify problems and determine specific
	action plans to solve them.

	<P>

	<LI>Provide all city residents with safe, revitalized neighborhoods and
	resources, including accessible and affordable housing, quality schools,
	employment, child care, transportation, and viable shopping areas and
	recreational facilities.

	<P>

	<LI>Develop a sense of community, increase economic integration and home
	ownership, and reduce crime.
</UL>

<P>The program is structured so that each of the 81 neighborhoods in Minneapolis
will conduct a workshop to identify issues and formulate plans to resolve the
problems identified.

<P>

<HR>

<ADDRESS>
<P><B>Neighborhood Revitalization Program</B><BR>
Crown Roller Mill, Suite 425<BR>
105 5 Av S<BR>
Minneapolis, MN 55401-2585
</ADDRESS>

<P><B>Phone Number</B><BR>
(612) 673-5140


<!-- #include "city_navbar.incl" -->
<P><HR>

