Citizen Participation requirements, to receive public comments on the proposed
use of funds for the Citys FY97 Consolidated Plan for HUDs Federal CDBG,
HOME, ESGP, and HOPWA entitlement funding based on the Mayors Budget Recommendations,
revisions as a result of intended reprogramming actions, and a proposed
revised Citizen Participation Plan. The hearing will be held at 5:05 p.m.
on Wednesday, December 4, 1996 in Room 317 City Hall, 350 South 5th Street.
The room is handicapped accessible.<BR>
