Agency (MCDA), and the Minneapolis Public Housing Authority (MPHA) invite
you to participate in the development of the Citys FY97 Consolidated Plan
for the Community Development Block Grant (CDBG), HOME Investment Partnerships
Program (HOME), Emergency Shelter Grants Program (ESGP), and the Housing
Opportunities for Persons with AIDS (HOPWA).<BR>
<BR>
The FY97 Consolidated Year is June 1, 1997 through May 31, 1998. You can
participate by attending the public hearing, by speaking at the hearing,
and/or by submitting written comments before, during, or after the hearing.
