block on South Nicollet Mall.</P>

<P>- Approved actions related to clean up of hazardous soils at the Watkins
and Schnitzer sites in the South East Minneapolis Industrial area.</P>

<P>- Appropriated funds for asbestos remediation at the Milwaukee Depot
site.</P>

<P>- Appropriated funds for soil correction costs for housing in the Hiawatha
Corridor.</P>

