to Summit Academy for youth employment services in the Central and Bryant
neighborhoods; also authorized contract with Hennepin County to receive
NRP funds and issue funds to Summit Academy for summer youth services.</P>

<P>- Gave conceptual approval of proposal to lease City-controlled channels
to Paragon Cable.</P>

<P>- Approved agreement with Minneapolis Police Officers Federation regarding
modifications to Permanent Shift memorandum of understanding.</P>

<P><B>ZONING &amp; PLANNING</B></P>

