<H1>NORTHRIDGE : an earthquake near Los Angeles</H1>

<IMG SRC="/icones/line_fusee.gif"><BR>

Northridge earthquake of January 17, 1994 had a magnitude of M = 6.7. <P>

To measure the deformation, interference patterns from the difference of two synthetic aperture radar images acquired before (orbit : 6653) and after (orbit : 13243) the earthquake by <A HREF="http://hdsn.eoc.nasda.go.jp/guide/guide/satellite/satdata/jers_e.html">JERS-1</A> satellite have been used. <P>

The epicentral area was located on lat : 34.2 N and long : -118.5 W. <P>


