<HEAD>
<TITLE>French Processing and Archiving Center</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="/icones/back8.gif">
<A NAME = "TOP"></A>
<PRE><img src="/images/fpac1.gif">    <img src="/images/cnes.gif"></PRE><P><P>
<H1>The French Processing and Archiving Center : F-PAC/ENVISAT</H1>
<IMG SRC="/icones/line_fusee.gif"><BR>

The F-PAC is the french element of the ENVISAT Payload Data Segment dedicated to off-line geophysical processing and archiving of the altimetric payload instruments including precise orbitography (i.e. RA-2, MWR and DORIS), and ASAR-Wave instrument. The F-PAC will be co-located at CNES in Toulouse and IFREMER in Brest.<BR>
Services to be offered by the F-PAC to users through a standard User Service Facility, are inventories and ordering facilities, Guide and Directory Services and dissemination on various medias. <P>

