<HEAD>
<TITLE>The TOPEX/POSEIDON Mission</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="/icones/back8.gif">
<PRE><IMG SRC="/images/topex2.gif">       <IMG SRC="/images/cnes.gif"></PRE></PRE>
<H1>TOPEX/POSEIDON</H1>
<IMG SRC="/icones/line_fusee.gif"><BR>
<P>
<H2>Table of Contents</H2>
