<HEAD>
<TITLE>Zoom Site de Fawnskin</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="/icones/back8.gif">
<IMG SRC="/icones/logo_radar.gif" ALIGN=LEFT> 
<H1>LANDERS : Zoom on Fawnskin area</H1>

<IMG SRC="/icones/line_fusee.gif"><BR>

Zoom of Fawnskin area, a zone of 8 km wide, the concentric fringes shows an earth inflating (M = 5.4). One cycle of colour corresponds to one interferometric fringe equivalent to 28 mm of change in the range between the satellite and the reflector on the ground. <P>

<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="/images/zoom_landers.gif"> <P>
<IMG SRC="/images/zoom_landers_logo.gif"> <P>
