<HEAD>
<TITLE>Etna  Model and Interferogram</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="/icones/back8.gif">
<IMG SRC="/icones/logo_radar.gif" ALIGN=LEFT> 
<H1>ETNA : Model and Interferogram</H1>

<IMG SRC="/icones/line_fusee.gif"><BR>

The modelled deformation, based on the change of pressure in a sphere located in an elastic half-space, increases linearly with time until the end of the eruption. <P>

<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="/images/etnamodl.gif"> <P>
</CENTER> <P>

The interferogram obtained with radar images. <P>

<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="/images/etna9.gif"> <P>
