<TR><TH ROWSPAN=6 ALIGN=CENTER>3<TD ALIGN=CENTER>Radiation<BR>budget and <BR>clouds<TD ALIGN=CENTER>synthesis<TD ALIGN=CENTER>global<BR>/ monthly<TD ALIGN=CENTER>9 x 9<TD ALIGN=CENTER>CD-ROM<TD ALIGN=CENTER>63
