<TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER>aerosol parameters<TD ALIGN=CENTER>global<BR>/ monthly<TD ALIGN=CENTER>3 x 3<TD ALIGN=CENTER>CD-ROM<TD ALIGN=CENTER>64
<TR><TD ROWSPAN=3 ALIGN=CENTER>Land surfaces<BR>and Aerosols<BR>over land<TD ALIGN=CENTER>albedo and NDVI<BR>parameters<TD ALIGN=CENTER>global<BR>/ 3 per month<TD ALIGN=CENTER>1 x 1<TD ALIGN=CENTER>CD-ROM<TD ALIGN=CENTER>104
<TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER>directional signature<BR>parameters<TD ALIGN=CENTER>global<BR>/ 3 per month<TD ALIGN=CENTER>1 x 1<TD ALIGN=CENTER>CD-ROM<TD ALIGN=CENTER>256
<TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER>atmospheric<BR>parameters<TD ALIGN=CENTER>global<BR>/ 3 per month<TD ALIGN=CENTER>3 x 3<TD ALIGN=CENTER>CD-ROM<TD ALIGN=CENTER>18
</TABLE></CENTER> <P>
* Data subsets can be provided either on DLT or EXABYTE<BR>
** All datasets for one product type during a given period (subscribing capability)<BR>
All POLDER products are projected on a geocoded sinusoidal area projection grid of 6.17 km resolution<P>
<P>

<A HREF="#TOP"> Back to contents </A><P>

<A NAME="data"><H2>Data policy</H2></A>
<BR>
<CENTER><TABLE BORDER>
<TR><TD>RESTRICTED USE<TD>Peaceful purposes<BR>Non-commercial utilization<BR>No release of POLDER Products to third parties excepted co-Is under conditions
<TR><TD>DISTRIBUTION POLICY<TD>Non validated data to PIs only<BR>Validated data released to the general user community as soon as possible
<TR><TD>PRICE POLICY<TD>Free for PIs<BR>At more than the cost to fulfill the request for the general user community
<TR><TD>LICENSE FOR USE<TD>All users should commit to respect  the data policy:<BR> - Special license for use for POLDER PIs<BR> - Standard license for the other users
</TABLE></CENTER>

<P>
