<HEAD>
<TITLE>Continuity of observations</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="/icones/back8.gif">
<IMG SRC="/images/plaket31.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"><P>
<H1>MEDIAS: Continuity of observations</H1>
<IMG SRC="/icones/line_fusee.gif"><BR>
The general objectives are to determine the long term trends for the main climatic parameters in the region, to gather the necessary input or validation data for numerical models, and to validate space observations. Measurements of atmospheric chemistry (e.g., tropospheric ozone, precipitation), radiation and aerosols are among the first priorities.
<P>
Within the framework of MEDIAS, it is intended to complete the existing ground-station networks and to document some <A HREF="geobio.html">IGBP</A> pilot-sites. <P>

