<TITLE>Data management</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="/icones/back8.gif">
<CENTER><IMG SRC="/images/plaket41.gif"></CENTER><P>
<H1>DATA MANAGEMENT</H1>
<IMG SRC="/icones/line_fusee.gif"><BR>
The crucial role of data and information systems and the importamce of data management methodologies in support of global change research are now clearly recognised. The large variety of types and sources of global, regional, and local data needs to strengthen data management programme and accessibility, to extend database directory, and to foster data exchange.<BR>

Information distribution facilities to the MEDIAS research community are being implemented (MEDIAS Newsletter, electronic mail) and data bases (e.g <A HREF="http://www.orstom.fr/hapex/index.html">Hapex-Sahel</A>, pilot sites, climate data series) are implemented. <P>

