<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE> WINDII Scientific Results</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="/icones/back8.gif">
<A NAME="Results"></A>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/cnes.gif"></CENTER>
<H1>WINDII Scientific Results</H1>
<IMG SRC="/icones/line_fusee.gif"><BR>
<H2>Scientifics Results</H2>
These results were obtained by Service d'Aeronomie CNRS France.<P>

<IMG SRC="/images/wzonal.gif" ALT="Wind Velocity"><P>
<EM>Wind velocity on Zonal component nearness equinox according to latitude</EM><P>

<IMG SRC="/icones/line_fusee.gif"><BR>

<IMG SRC="/images/wmerid.gif" ALT="Wind Velocity"><P>
<EM>Wind velocity on Meridional component nearness equinox according to latitude</EM><P>

<A HREF="Mission.html#Description"> Back to index</A> <P>

