<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT12-B38-361</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA078-000532-B041-335</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www-projet.cst.cnes.fr:8060/oersted/Spaceseg.html 132.149.93.1 19970124125145 text/html 6424
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
MIME-Version: 1.0
