<DOCOLDNO>IA078-000532-B042-195</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www-projet.cst.cnes.fr:8060/strateole/Objectives.html 132.149.93.1 19970124125731 text/html 4354
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
MIME-Version: 1.0
