<DOCNO>WT12-B38-373</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA078-000532-B042-212</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www-projet.cst.cnes.fr:8060/strateole/description.html 132.149.93.1 19970124125743 text/html 5733
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: CERN/3.0
