<HEAD>
<TITLE>CNES Contribution</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="/icones/back8.gif">
<CENTER><img src="/images/cnes.gif"></CENTER>

<H1>CNES Contribution</H1>

<IMG SRC="/icones/line_fusee.gif"><BR>

CNES Contribution: the French CNES SeaWIFS service CNES presently develops a SeaWIFS data and products information service restricted to the french SeaWIFS science investigators selected by <A HREF="http://seawifs.gsfc.nasa.gov:80/SEAWIFS.html">NASA</A>. It is part of an Ocean Color Data and Information Service. <P>

<!--<IMG SRC="/icones/line_fusee.gif"><BR>-->
