<DOCOLDNO>IA078-000532-B043-147</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www-projet.cst.cnes.fr:8060/polder/Science.html 132.149.93.1 19970124130312 text/html 14769
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
