<H1>Weather Page</H1>

<H3>Last updated at 22:58 UTC Wednesday 8th January</H3>

<BR>

<img SRC="/pics/ftt4.gif">

<A HREF="//www.shetland-news.co.uk/websites/bressaboats/"><img src="/bressaboats/bressaboats.jpg" hspace=2></A>

<img SRC="/pics/ftt5.gif">

<A HREF="//www.shetland-news.co.uk/websites/amenity/"><img src="/amenity/amenity.gif" hspace=2></A>

