<P>
<H1>Lady Godiva </H1>
<H2>An irregular magazine from Sanday, Orkney. </H2>
<HR>
<P>
</center>

<P><A HREF="stockton.jpg"><IMG ALIGN=right SRC="stockton.jpg" border=0></A>

<H3><P>
