<center>
<H4>
<IMG SRC="/pics/header.gif">
<BR>
<I>'Great is the Truth, and it will prevail'</I>
<P>

<H1><FONT COLOR="#008000"><U>Welcome to the 'Green Room'</U></FONT></H1>
<IMG SRC="/pics/revolveworld.gif" WIDTH=64 HEIGHT=64 BORDER=0 align=left>
<IMG SRC="/pics/revolveworld.gif" WIDTH=64 HEIGHT=64 BORDER=0 align=right>
<H2><FONT COLOR="#008000">A Forum for Environmental Issues</FONT>
<BR><FONT COLOR="#008000" size=4>with extensive links to other sites worldwide</FONT>

<BR clear=all>

<img width=75% height=3 src="/pics/thinbar.gif">
</CENTER>
</H2>
<P>

<CENTER>
<TABLE border=0>
<TH colspan=3 align=center>
<FONT SIZE=3 COLOR="#006400"><img src="/pics/blank.gif" WIDTH=15 HEIGHT=1 BORDER=0>Click on the <img border=0 src="/pics/cube.gif"> to go to that section<P></FONT>
<th>
<TR>
<TD><a href="latest.html"><img border=0 src="/pics/cube.gif"></a></TD><TD ALIGN=left NOWRAP><img src="/pics/blank.gif" WIDTH=15 HEIGHT=1 BORDER=0><FONT SIZE=5 COLOR="#006400"><a href="latest.html"><B>Latest News & Comment</B></a><IMG SRC="/pics/blank.gif" WIDTH=180 HEIGHT=1 BORDER=0><BR></FONT></TD><TD></TD>
</TR>

<TR>
<TD></TD><TD ALIGN=right NOWRAP><FONT SIZE=5 COLOR="#006400"><a href="oil.html"><B>Oil Pollution</B></a></FONT><img src="/pics/blank.gif" WIDTH=15 HEIGHT=1 BORDER=0></TD><TD><a href="oil.html"><img border=0 src="/pics/cube.gif"></a><BR></TD>
