<P>
<H1> Oldest Shetlander dies
</H1>
<H2></H2>
<img SRC="/pics/ftt6.gif">
<img SRC="/pics/ftt7.gif">
<img SRC="/pics/ftt8.gif">
<img SRC="/pics/ftt9.gif">
<img SRC="/pics/ftt5.gif">
<HR>
</center>
<P>

<P>
10th January 1997
<P>
Shetland's oldest resident, Mrs Maggie Jarmson, has died at the age  of 104. Mrs Jarmson, a great, great grandmother, had been housebound  for some years at her home in the village of Walls.
<P>
The funeral will be held tomorrow [SAT] from Selivoe Gospel Hall to  the Gruting churchyard.
<P>




<P>
<BR clear=all>
